it affects graphics/librsvg2-rust

A quick workaround is to patch 
/usr/ports/lang/rust/work/rustc-1.54.0-src/src/llvm-project/compiler-rt/lib/builtins/cpu_model.c

and replace (around line 781):
unsigned long hwcap = getauxval(AT_HWCAP);
__aarch64_have_lse_atomics = (hwcap & HWCAP_ATOMICS) != 0;


with
//  unsigned long hwcap = getauxval(AT_HWCAP);
//  __aarch64_have_lse_atomics = (hwcap & HWCAP_ATOMICS) != 0;
  __aarch64_have_lse_atomics = 0;

Then rebuild lang/rust.

I'll try to implement a better patch soon.
